    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《迷失异常》中，你在一座未知建筑的 9 楼醒来。你的目标是到达一楼并逃离这里。要离开这里，您必须检测并标记异常情况。如果您标记了所有异常情况，电梯将带您前往下层。你应该仔细检查每个地方并进行相应标记，因为如果你错过了异常情况，电梯就会带你回到9楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312120/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.poster.avif?t=1747270010\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312120/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.webm?t=1747270010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312120/extras/5099137edb96e2ac8c09c3741b29777b.mp4?t=1747270010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏时间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15-30分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现并标记每层楼的不同异常现象。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些异常现象只能用紫外线手电筒才能看到。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入考验您观察能力的游戏体验。</p></li></ul>",
